@startuml 08-admin-stats
title Sơ đồ tuần tự - Dashboard Thống kê giao dịch (Admin)

show footbox

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.2
skinparam roundCorner 8
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8DC
skinparam noteBorderColor #C0A030

actor "Admin" as User
participant "Front-end\n(StatsDashboard)" as FE
participant "API Gateway" as GW
participant "User Service" as US
participant "Transaction\nService" as TS
database "user_db" as UDB
database "transaction_db" as TDB

== 1. Admin vào trang Thống kê ==
User -> FE : Click menu "Thống kê"\n→ trang load

note right of FE #FFF3E0
  **State khởi tạo:**
  - preset = "30d"
  - from = hôm nay − 29 ngày
  - to = hôm nay
  - granularity = "day"
  useEffect mount → gọi fetchAll()
end note

note right of FE #E8F5E9
  **FE gọi 2 API song song (Promise.all):**
  - getOverview(from, to)
  - getTimeSeries(granularity, from, to)
end note

== 2. Gateway xác thực JWT + role ADMIN ==

FE -> GW : GET /api/v1/transactions/dashboard/overview\n  ?from=...&to=...\nAuthorization: Bearer <JWT>

note right of GW #FFEBEE
  **Bảo mật 2 lớp:**
  (1) AuthGlobalFilter:
      Decode JWT, validate jti với user-service
      Inject X-User-Id / Role / Phone

  (2) SecurityConfig: path
      /api/v1/transactions/dashboard/**
      → hasAuthority("ADMIN")
      User thường gọi → 403 Forbidden
end note

GW -> US : GET /internal/users/validate?jti=...
US -> UDB : SELECT FROM invalidated_tokens
UDB --> US : (rỗng → còn hiệu lực)
US --> GW : 200 OK

alt JWT.role ≠ "ADMIN"
    GW --> FE : 403 ACCESS_DENIED
    FE --> User : "Bạn không có quyền truy cập"
end

GW -> TS : GET /api/transactions/dashboard/overview\n+ header X-User-Role = "ADMIN"

note right of TS #FFEBEE
  **Double-check ở Controller:**
  Controller cũng kiểm tra
  UserContext.getRole() == "ADMIN"
  → defense in depth
end note

== 3. Service tổng hợp KPI (3 query DB tuần tự) ==

note right of TS #FFF3E0
  **TransactionStatsService.getOverview:**
  Service gọi 3 query DB tuần tự, gộp kết quả
  thành 1 StatsOverviewResponse.
end note

TS -> TDB : (1) aggregateOverviewKpis(from, to)\n[native SQL với FILTER]
TDB --> TS : { total, success_count, failed_count,\n  total_volume, total_fee }

note right of TDB #FFF3E0
  **Native SQL gộp 5 KPI trong 1 query:**
  COUNT(*),
  COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE status='SUCCESS'),
  COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE status='FAILED'),
  COALESCE(SUM(amount) FILTER (status=SUCCESS), 0),
  COALESCE(SUM(fee) FILTER (status=SUCCESS), 0)
  FROM transactions
  WHERE created_at BETWEEN :from AND :to
end note

TS -> TDB : (2) countGroupByType(from, to) [JPQL]
TDB --> TS : List<[type, count]>

TS -> TDB : (3) countGroupByStatus(from, to) [JPQL]
TDB --> TS : List<[status, count]>

note right of TS #FFF3E0
  **Post-processing:**
  - successRate = successCount / total
  - byType: fill 0 cho enum không có data
    (TRANSFER, PAYMENT, TOPUP)
  - byStatus: fill 0 cho enum không có data
    (SUCCESS, PENDING, FAILED, CANCELLED)
end note

TS --> FE : 200 StatsOverviewResponse\n{ totalTransactions, totalVolume,\n  totalFee, successCount, successRate,\n  byType{...}, byStatus{...} }

== 4. Song song - lấy time-series ==

FE -> GW : GET /api/v1/transactions/dashboard/timeseries\n  ?granularity=day&from=...&to=...
GW -> TS : (đã verify JWT + ADMIN role ở bước 2)

TS -> TS : Validate granularity ∈\n{day, week, month}

alt granularity không hợp lệ
    TS --> FE : 400 INVALID_REQUEST
end

TS -> TDB : aggregateTimeSeries(granularity, from, to)

note right of TDB #FFF3E0
  **Native SQL với generate_series:**
  WITH series AS (
    SELECT generate_series(
      DATE_TRUNC(:granularity, :from),
      DATE_TRUNC(:granularity, :to),
      CAST('1 ' || :granularity AS interval)
    ) AS period
  )
  SELECT s.period, COUNT(t.id), COALESCE(SUM(t.amount), 0)
  FROM series s
  LEFT JOIN transactions t
    ON DATE_TRUNC(:granularity, t.created_at) = s.period
    AND t.status = 'SUCCESS'
    AND t.created_at BETWEEN :from AND :to
  GROUP BY s.period ORDER BY s.period

  → Fill 0 cho period không có giao dịch
     (tránh biểu đồ bị "thủng" lỗ)
end note

TDB --> TS : List<[period, count, volume]>
TS --> FE : 200 List<TimeSeriesPoint>\n[{ period, count, volume }, ...]

== 5. Front-end render UI ==
note right of FE #FFF3E0
  **Recharts render:**
  - 4 KPI cards (totalTransactions, totalVolume,
    totalFee, successRate)
  - LineChart: trục X = period, Y = volume
  - 2 PieChart: byType + byStatus
    (kèm legend với % và số GD)
end note

FE --> User : Hiển thị toàn bộ dashboard

== 6. Admin đổi filter / granularity ==
User -> FE : Click "7 ngày" / chọn date range\nhoặc đổi granularity (Ngày/Tuần/Tháng)

note right of FE #E8F5E9
  State từ/to/granularity thay đổi
  → useCallback dependency thay đổi
  → useEffect tự gọi lại fetchAll()
end note

FE -> GW : Gọi lại 2 endpoint với param mới
GW -> TS : (lặp lại quy trình 2 → 4)
TS --> FE : 200 (data mới)
FE --> User : Cập nhật chart + KPI

@enduml
